							<span class="tag-links">
				<span class="entry-utility-prep entry-utility-prep-tag-links">Tagged</span> <a href="http://anniemachon.ch/annie_machon/tag/elizabeth-murray" rel="tag">Elizabeth Murray</a>, <a href="http://anniemachon.ch/annie_machon/tag/integrity" rel="tag">integrity</a>, <a href="http://anniemachon.ch/annie_machon/tag/intelligence-2" rel="tag">intelligence</a>, <a href="http://anniemachon.ch/annie_machon/tag/iran" rel="tag">Iran</a>, <a href="http://anniemachon.ch/annie_machon/tag/julian-assange" rel="tag">Julian Assange</a>, <a href="http://anniemachon.ch/annie_machon/tag/ray-mcgovern" rel="tag">Ray McGovern</a>, <a href="http://anniemachon.ch/annie_machon/tag/tom-fingar" rel="tag">Tom Fingar</a>, <a href="http://anniemachon.ch/annie_machon/tag/war" rel="tag">war</a>, <a href="http://anniemachon.ch/annie_machon/tag/whistleblowers-2" rel="tag">whistleblowers</a>, <a href="http://anniemachon.ch/annie_machon/tag/wikileaks" rel="tag">Wikileaks</a>			</span>
						
