							<span class="tag-links">
				<span class="entry-utility-prep entry-utility-prep-tag-links">Tagged</span> <a href="http://anniemachon.ch/annie_machon/tag/annie-machon" rel="tag">Annie Machon</a>, <a href="http://anniemachon.ch/annie_machon/tag/har" rel="tag">HAR</a>, <a href="http://anniemachon.ch/annie_machon/tag/julian-assange" rel="tag">Julian Assange</a>, <a href="http://anniemachon.ch/annie_machon/tag/whistleblowers-2" rel="tag">whistleblowers</a>, <a href="http://anniemachon.ch/annie_machon/tag/wikileaks" rel="tag">Wikileaks</a>			</span>
						
